---
import ZhLayout from '../../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout title="静电控制技术指南 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="史帝克静电知识库：什么是ESD、如何防止静电、ESD控制产品选型、工业静电消除解决方案，适用于电子、显示屏和工业制造环境。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/guides">
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/static-eliminator/bg-2.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; background-attachment: fixed;">
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="600">技术知识库</span>
      <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="100">静电控制技术指南</h1>
      <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="200">
        适用于工业制造环境的静电放电技术指南：什么是ESD、静电防护方法、ESD控制产品选型及工业静电消除解决方案。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px; padding: 60px 20px;">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 28px;">

        <a href="/zh/guides/what-is-esd" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">什么是静电放电（ESD）？</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">ESD定义、产生原因、如何损坏电子元件，以及工业ESD防护标准。</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">阅读指南 →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/guides/how-to-prevent-static" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="80" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">如何防止静电</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">实用静电防护方法：接地、离子化、湿度控制、防静电材料和操作规范。</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">阅读指南 →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/guides/esd-control-products" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="160" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">ESD控制产品选型指南</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">离子棒、离子风机、离子风枪的产品介绍及选型方法，帮您找到最适合的防静电设备。</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">阅读指南 →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/guides/industrial-static-eliminator" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="240" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">工业静电消除解决方案</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">按行业分类的静电消除应用——电子、显示屏、印刷、塑料和洁净室制造环境的产品选型指导。</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">阅读指南 →</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
